name: GuitarKingVR
summary: GuitarKingVR is the ultimate guitar simulation. Play different songs in different locations. Show your skills, grab the right chords, rock like hell. GuitarKingVR is more than just playing air guitar, you get what you play! The flying picks show you the way, anyone can become a Guitar King. Switch from beginner to rockstar mode and show the world your skills. Are you ready to...
